data.value:
You and your company can support tools in a more official way rather than just donating via PayPal or 'Buy Me a Coffee'.
Supporting is not just giving money; it means you or your company gain in time and quality by using these tools. If we get something, we want to give back—to support their development and maintenance.
You will receive an official receipt automatically and, if needed, an invoice. Supporting can be done with a credit card. Other options will be available depending on your location. Stripe handles the payment.
If you want to read about my thoughts, click the link below!
